Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:01.90,title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\blur2\pos(226.143,571.714)}化作風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾  蘿潔怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:01:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是昏過去了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  下山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去追災禍的現主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔的情況怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體到處都在抽筋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用待在蘿潔身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在史雷正在給她施加加護
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想借你那把號稱能殺龍的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一場戰鬥將會是最終之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要將那些龍全部淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再走到災禍的現主那裡是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然在瑞迪雷克他們確實淨化了龍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只淨化了一條龍就消耗成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許在將來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷可以成為能淨化這些龍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也認同這點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷的強大不容置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,災禍的現主肯定會讓汙穢覆蓋世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是擔心一下自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你這模樣站著都很勉強了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的槍借給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若世界的汙穢都聚集到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只要我們在這裡清除它們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世界就能煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說這才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想實現蘿潔所盼望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是為你自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了伊安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會死在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這人  他在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能就這麼不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帶他回去  好好安葬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種北極之地  竟然會有城市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是冰雪之城梅爾西恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿越這座城後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是有著地脈熔點的奇拉拉烏斯火山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,災禍的現主就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記述上寫著這裡曾是個繁華昌盛的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在變成廢墟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過人類已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是諾爾敏天族格瑞莫爾  導師大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道我是導師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我都活了多少年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是來淨化災禍的現主的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪吹得這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這閒聊可要凍死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到竟然能在這種地方見到格瑞莫爾大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好感動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們撐到今天也不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能問你點事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊菈你讀過這本書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這書上寫的這個世界的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有天族的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是問卡奴努西和五大神的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前任導師米凱爾大人認為是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡奴努西和五大神是天族最尊貴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們要前往的地脈熔點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是他們的大本營之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為災禍的現主前往那裡並非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讀過這本書後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得假如貝爾貝特·庫羅沒有心生憎恨的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界是不是就不會爆發災難了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那犧牲她弟弟來拯救世界的阿爾特留斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他所做的事就是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只要戰爭一爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實就會有成千上萬的人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什麼才是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼才是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷你覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們應該還有更多互相理解的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不再重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須認識更多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,導師踏上旅途  見識各式各樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所想所悟的  才是真正的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這麼相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷  肚子餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽你這麼一說就餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有湯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯  就來點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  格瑞莫爾大姐是說諾爾敏天族還有未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟導師大人一起  當然有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這就是所謂的憑魔  汙穢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你們上茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂瑟爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛倫斯的騎士團長喝個茶這麼窩囊好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是男人就…好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔  你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又在神依後昏過去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你神依戰鬥的時間比我長好幾倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有湯  你喝得下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時不用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想過天族為什麼會存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛  我記得好像五百年前左右煩惱過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那抱歉了  跟你提這種青春煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我聽聽你的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們天族以人類的祈禱為糧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,施以加護  維持世界的均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若這就是天族的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們到底是為了什麼而誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  想這種事有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看著蘿潔就會想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎樣才算活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想讓她死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據書上所著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾貝特離開這個世界已有千年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷你覺得能淨化災禍的現主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難說啊  老實說我也沒把握
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那汙穢太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全想像不出到底藏有多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾貝特·庫羅之後怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  天遺見聞錄上沒有更多記載了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔或許沒辦法繼續下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是恢復需要時間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把她留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許這才是對她好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好你個頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下  給我一碗湯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我落得這副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也用不著你替我著想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神依我也能繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我發誓  帶上我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然還會笑成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是蘿潔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺已經想通了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼鳥要飛上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳥  只是想飛就飛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算沒有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算可能會折斷翅膀摔死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不為別人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是自己想飛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才會飛上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走上自己堅信的道路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您認識他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  他死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這前面就我們幾個過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  真的很感謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然你們看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這裡有五位可靠的伙伴跟我們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為有各位同行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的旅途才那樣美好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類和天族可以共存
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這段時光讓我深感如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去淨化災禍的現主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重造世界的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是汙穢的花路一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在請我們進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有援兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  是西蒙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就送你上路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷  如果你把力量浪費在淨化這些龍上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就無法與在前方的災禍的現主戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不過了這關就見不到災禍的現主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輪到這傢伙出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾  那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札維塔  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我從札維塔那借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用這傢伙幹掉龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要淨化災禍的現主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓汙穢從世上消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我會全部淨化給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這數量你辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此也不能殺它們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行我也要試試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時可以進行神依
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就擔任防守好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汙穢就交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎麼做  德澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也跟他們一個意見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你們全都被導師感化了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  我早就覺得會這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都不願意殺它們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札維塔  不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  接下來該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的風來吹飛這些傢伙好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個  注意別被捲進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要創造個美好的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔  來神依
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯維尤=尤克姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔  聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就這樣撞進龍群中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後支援我就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中心對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在跟誰說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能到這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了  中心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好壯觀的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔  我將化為風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的一切吹飛它們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔  這麼多年謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  連謝謝都不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是  你幹嘛突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂德澤爾  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它來了  就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用不著哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我的交情  不就幾個月嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還這麼小的時候我就看著你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴史雷  我死不是他的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是導師不惜犧牲他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就會重蹈歷史的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就會從這世上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最後請允許我向你懺悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我憑依在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把布拉德的理想強加給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懷著本不需要的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經歷了許多痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連殺人  都利用了你的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那種事  沒那種事啊 德澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這夢想的契機是德澤爾給我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我會感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  會為懷著這夢想的布拉德和德澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我發誓一定會實現這個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  德澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿潔  你這傢伙真是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  蘿潔
